30 nine through twelve (9-12).
31 (b) However, this section shall not apply to a:
32 (1) Student with an individualized education program if the
33 student's individualized education program includes a course recovery
34 program;
35 (2) Student who is in foster care;
36 (3) Student who is in the custody of the Division of Youth
